{"tid":1742742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日只做一件事","createTime":"2019-11-21T02:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T02:17:44.000Z","uid":173883,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9deed1d558c3106074ac18e5e76e2df1c4d5c578","tid":1742742,"uid":173883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:10:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投票</span></span></strong><br />\n而家一路睇緊立法會緊急質詢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有建制都吹風驚星期日會有暴力事件發生</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">證明星期日一定有狗/大陸狗/藍絲扮示威者搞破壞</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以我地應該有共識星期日只做一件事 投票</span></span><br />\n由星期六開始不堵路不裝修與民休息齊準備投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />星期日全民街坊裝7:30開始冇口罩落樓投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">邊個搞鳩亂星期六日就證明左係港共主動延遲區選</span></span><br />\n想賴落我地度？收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b938b24ffc3c2d184045a7cf1517a017122355d","tid":1742742,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:10:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期日記住投票</span></span><br />\n阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1399f12de3dcd4b0060563a5c5513bfefc079b5a","tid":1742742,"uid":173883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:10:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7205639b8a86d3f856aacff9225459abcde853a1","tid":1742742,"uid":173883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:10:43.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"0649c56dd2853b440c9e37c61317a